{"tid":2229330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中秋節囚犯獲加餸 有雞脾及雪梨","createTime":"2020-10-04T10:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T13:12:07.000Z","uid":66271,"like":29,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f563dcdb4f559f6822e78b6a72ec92fb2561c2e4","tid":2229330,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:08:30.000Z","msg":"過去中秋夜，人月應兩團圓，但一眾囚犯身在牢中未能與家人團聚。懲教署特別為約7000名囚犯「加餸」，有雞脾食，又有雪梨，以及由非牟利機構捐贈的月餅，希望他們感受到節日氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n其中囚於壁屋懲教所的森仔，自幼在單親家庭中長大，森仔起初未有體恤母親的辛勞，只覺她嘮嘮叨叨，即使過時過節，森仔都出外消遣，少有回家，後來誤交損友，誤入歧途，最終因「販運危險藥物」罪被判監。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/10/20201004_po_%E6%87%B2%E6%95%99%E7%BD%B21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F10%2F20201004_po_%25E6%2587%25B2%25E6%2595%2599%25E7%25BD%25B21.jpg&h=c8ceeeb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n懲教署中秋為約7000名在囚人士「加餸」，並派發由非牟利機構捐贈的月餅。<br />\n<br />\n他在獄中重拾課本，亦接受不同的職業訓練，後悔當時沒聽母親的教訓，最終犯事入獄，今年佳節他仍身在牢中，會好好珍惜手中的月餅，及珍惜以後每一個改過自新的機會。"},{"pid":"0a03f2c3154d796349e0ebf7517adebccbe9eff2","tid":2229330,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:11:50.000Z","msg":"Dllm 豉油脾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b01bb6ab4fede15cb874102afe22d195992a0890","tid":2229330,"uid":135867,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:14:55.000Z","msg":"瘦弱啲既會唔會無得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd3c47bc6d4b646a5976aef272420de168106e6","tid":2229330,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:16:35.000Z","msg":"手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5519971b739018d29aaa7752df0a2cdd62d2b14d","tid":2229330,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:17:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" cl